{"tid":165274,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"涉棄圖書館簡體字書　熱血公民鄭錦滿被控盜竊周四提堂","createTime":"2017-03-21T08:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T12:05:41.000Z","uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c657ab1bf7db9ffdaeb23060084d8dddfea6fe4","tid":165274,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"「熱血公民」昨日於Facebook發文，指該副主席鄭錦滿因早前在圖書館拍片，籲市民用「自己方式」將簡體字書下架，昨日被警方拘捕帶往元朗警署，並落案控以「盜竊罪」，將於本週四在九龍城裁判院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n　　人稱「四眼哥哥」的熱血公民成員鄭錦滿於去年4月2日拍片，示範在公共圖書館搜集簡體字書籍並將其銷毀，包括在隱蔽處扔掉，如放在消防喉隱蔽地方、垃圾桶及圖書館書櫃與牆壁間空隙中，涉及書籍逾20本。去年4月他曾被警方網絡安全及科技罪案組人員拘捕，涉觸犯不誠實使用電腦及盜竊罪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43000b787d7c33d5d12817cdd398245ee7b076de","tid":165274,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aee02c9a567c1a051bf39b465a6cf36e594d2e2","tid":165274,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:56:40.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"9590917b544bede10232686b8912a57ee37147a0","tid":165274,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>B</blockquote><br />\nO"},{"pid":"396f51f0cc17a45c2c098d53333a9d12821c33aa","tid":165274,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"衰係d on9野到佢都算搞笑"},{"pid":"a16d9e94f9e7874b3e30183663ea9b0987246705","tid":165274,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衰係d on9野到佢都算搞笑</blockquote><br />\n你隻五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6e0b9b6a7de3ba0b5a802695757fe08